              <span id="lbl_picurl"></span>
              <p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:方正小标宋简体">周至县人民医院</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:方正小标宋简体">网络安全等级保护测评项目中标结果公告</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 21px">一、项目名称：</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312">网络安全等级保护测评项目</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 21px">二、评审结果：</span></p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr style=";height:45px" class="firstRow"><td width="289" style="border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;" height="45"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-size:   16px;font-family:宋体">投标单位名称</span></strong></p></td><td width="141" style="border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0px 7px;" height="45"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-size:   16px;font-family:宋体">最终报价（万元）</span></strong></p></td><td style="border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0px 7px;" height="45" width="64"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-size:   16px;font-family:宋体">得分</span></strong></p></td><td width="101" style="border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0px 7px;" height="45"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:36px"><strong><span style="font-size:   16px;font-family:宋体">排名</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr style=";height:45px"><td width="289" style="border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-co